some unfinished business.

00:17:26.171 --> 00:17:29.257 position:50% align:center
[SUGIMOTO bellows]

00:17:29.341 --> 00:17:30.592 position:50% align:center
[GANSOKU]
What is this?

00:17:30.675 --> 00:17:33.553 position:50% align:center
