are full of rage.

00:17:33.636 --> 00:17:36.222 position:50% align:center
But he shouldn't feel
any anger towards me.

00:17:38.641 --> 00:17:39.934 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
Should we... help?

00:17:40.018 --> 00:17:41.853 position:50% align:center
Help who? Which one?

00:17:41.936 --> 00:17:46.024 position:50% align:center
We have to stop them.
We need Sugimoto to find Asirpa.

00:17:46.107 --> 00:17:47.859 position:50% align:center
We can't let him
take any more hits!

00:17:47.942 --> 00:17:49.527 position:50% align:center
[groans]

00:17:49.611 --> 00:17:52.947 position:50% align:center
[GANSOKU] Why is there
so much anger inside you?

00:17:53.031 --> 00:17:56.076 position:50% align:center
[SUGIMOTO grunting]

00:17:56.159 --> 00:17:57.994 position:50% align:center
[GANSOKU]
Who are you angry at?

00:17:58.078 --> 00:18:00.330 position:50% align:center
What is making you rage?

00:18:03.833 --> 00:18:05.043 position:50% align:center
[SUGIMOTO snarls]

00:18:05.126 --> 00:18:06.586 position:50% align:center
[GANSOKU grunts]

00:18:07.295 --> 00:18:09.381 position:50% align:center
[SUGIMOTO]
Asirpa...

00:18:09.464 --> 00:18:11.966 position:50% align:center
[GANSOKU grunts]

00:18:12.050 --> 00:18:14.260 position:50% align:center
I am...

00:18:14.344 --> 00:18:16.304 position:50% align:center
