00:18:24.479 --> 00:18:27.649 position:50% align:center
[SUGIMOTO]
I am... I am useless!

00:18:27.732 --> 00:18:30.193 position:50% align:center
[sobs]

00:18:30.276 --> 00:18:32.153 position:50% align:center
Forgive yourself.

00:18:32.237 --> 00:18:33.988 position:50% align:center
