wretched state you're in

00:18:34.072 --> 00:18:36.491 position:50% align:center
that you're giving it
everything you have.

00:18:37.951 --> 00:18:39.494 position:50% align:center
[GANSOKU snarls]

00:18:43.206 --> 00:18:45.375 position:50% align:center
[GANSOKU groans]

00:18:45.458 --> 00:18:47.711 position:50% align:center
[TANIGAKI]
That's enough! Stop this!

00:18:53.591 --> 00:18:55.927 position:50% align:center
[KOITO whimpers]

00:18:56.011 --> 00:18:57.053 position:50% align:center
Ah!

00:18:59.889 --> 00:19:01.099 position:50% align:center
Oh, god!

00:19:01.182 --> 00:19:03.852 position:50% align:center
It's so cold!

00:19:03.935 --> 00:19:06.771 position:50% align:center
[whimpering]

00:19:06.855 --> 00:19:08.189 position:50% align:center
--I'm freezing!
--So, uh...

00:19:08.273 --> 00:19:09.983 position:50% align:center
B-Back to the b-banya!

00:19:10.066 --> 00:19:11.317 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
Tsukishima..!

00:19:11.401 --> 00:19:13.737 position:50% align:center
