00:23:28.742 --> 00:23:31.202 position:50% align:center
Their fatty meat is
considered a delicacy.

00:23:31.286 --> 00:23:32.203 position:50% align:center
Try some.

00:23:32.287 --> 00:23:33.788 position:50% align:center
[SHIRAISHI]
Ahh...

